Choose 2. You may choose the same mode more than once;

* The next card you play this turn with an effect that deals arcane damage, instead deals that much arcane damage plus 1.

* Draw a card.

Whenever you play an attack action card with 6 or more base [attack], roll a 6 sided die. On;

* 1 to 4 - Half the attack's base [attack], rounded down.
* 5 or 6 - Double the attack's base [attack].

Choose 1;

* Target club or hammer attack gains +4[attack].
* Target attack action card with cost [2 resource] or greater gains +4[attack] and "If this hits, the defending hero discards a card."

Choose 1;

* Target club or hammer attack gains +3[attack].
* Target attack action card with cost [2 resource] or greater gains +3[attack] and "If this hits, the defending hero discards a card."

Choose 1;

* Target club or hammer attack gains +2[attack].
* Target attack action card with cost [2 resource] or greater gains +2[attack] and "If this hits, the defending hero discards a card."

Choose 1;

* Target sword or dagger attack gains +3[attack].
* Target attack action card with cost [resource] or less gains +3[attack] and "If this hits, this attack gains **go again**."

Choose 1;

* Target sword or dagger attack gains +2[attack].
* Target attack action card with cost [resource] or less gains +2[attack] and "If this hits, this attack gains **go again**."

Choose 1;

* Target sword or dagger attack gains +1[attack].
